{"word":"G5335 - φάσκω - pháskō - fas'-ko - Affirm","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">φάσκω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">pháskō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">fas'-ko</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Affirm</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - சொல், சாதி"},{"paragraph":"to affirm, allege, to pretend or profess"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Prolongation from the same as <a href=\"#/G5346 - φημί - phēmí - fay-mee'/5346\">G5346</a>; to <i>assert:</i> - affirm, profess, say.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}